# Debug規則 (Debug Rules)

## 日誌記錄系統

### 日誌級別定義
```php
const LOG_LEVELS = [
    'DEBUG' => 0,    // 詳細調試信息
    'INFO' => 1,     // 一般信息
    'WARNING' => 2,  // 警告信息
    'ERROR' => 3,    // 錯誤信息
    'CRITICAL' => 4  // 嚴重錯誤
];
```

### 日誌記錄器類
```php
class Logger {
    private $logFile;
    private $minLevel;
    
    public function __construct($logFile = 'app.log', $minLevel = 'INFO') {
        $this->logFile = __DIR__ . '/logs/' . $logFile;
        $this->minLevel = LOG_LEVELS[$minLevel];
        $this->ensureLogDirectory();
    }
    
    public function debug($message, $context = []) {
        $this->log('DEBUG', $message, $context);
    }
    
    public function info($message, $context = []) {
        $this->log('INFO', $message, $context);
    }
    
    public function warning($message, $context = []) {
        $this->log('WARNING', $message, $context);
    }
    
    public function error($message, $context = []) {
        $this->log('ERROR', $message, $context);
    }
    
    public function critical($message, $context = []) {
        $this->log('CRITICAL', $message, $context);
    }
    
    private function log($level, $message, $context) {
        if (LOG_LEVELS[$level] < $this->minLevel) {
            return;
        }
        
        $logEntry = [
            'timestamp' => date('Y-m-d H:i:s'),
            'level' => $level,
            'message' => $message,
            'context' => $context,
            'memory' => memory_get_usage(true),
            'file' => debug_backtrace()[2]['file'] ?? 'unknown',
            'line' => debug_backtrace()[2]['line'] ?? 0
        ];
        
        file_put_contents($this->logFile, json_encode($logEntry) . "\n", FILE_APPEND | LOCK_EX);
    }
}
```

## 錯誤追蹤系統

### 全局錯誤處理器
```php
class ErrorHandler {
    private $logger;
    
    public function __construct(Logger $logger) {
        $this->logger = $logger;
        $this->registerHandlers();
    }
    
    private function registerHandlers() {
        set_error_handler([$this, 'handleError']);
        set_exception_handler([$this, 'handleException']);
        register_shutdown_function([$this, 'handleShutdown']);
    }
    
    public function handleError($severity, $message, $file, $line) {
        $errorTypes = [
            E_ERROR => 'ERROR',
            E_WARNING => 'WARNING',
            E_NOTICE => 'INFO',
            E_USER_ERROR => 'ERROR',
            E_USER_WARNING => 'WARNING',
            E_USER_NOTICE => 'INFO'
        ];
        
        $level = $errorTypes[$severity] ?? 'ERROR';
        
        $this->logger->log($level, $message, [
            'file' => $file,
            'line' => $line,
            'severity' => $severity
        ]);
    }
    
    public function handleException($exception) {
        $this->logger->critical('未捕獲的異常', [
            'message' => $exception->getMessage(),
            'file' => $exception->getFile(),
            'line' => $exception->getLine(),
            'trace' => $exception->getTraceAsString()
        ]);
    }
    
    public function handleShutdown() {
        $error = error_get_last();
        if ($error && in_array($error['type'], [E_ERROR, E_CORE_ERROR, E_COMPILE_ERROR])) {
            $this->logger->critical('致命錯誤', $error);
        }
    }
}
```

## 調試工具

### 性能分析器
```php
class Profiler {
    private $startTime;
    private $checkpoints = [];
    
    public function start() {
        $this->startTime = microtime(true);
        $this->checkpoints = [];
    }
    
    public function checkpoint($name) {
        $this->checkpoints[$name] = [
            'time' => microtime(true) - $this->startTime,
            'memory' => memory_get_usage(true)
        ];
    }
    
    public function getReport() {
        $totalTime = microtime(true) - $this->startTime;
        $peakMemory = memory_get_peak_usage(true);
        
        return [
            'total_time' => $totalTime,
            'peak_memory' => $peakMemory,
            'checkpoints' => $this->checkpoints
        ];
    }
}
```

### 數據庫查詢調試
```php
class DatabaseDebugger {
    private $queries = [];
    private $logger;
    
    public function logQuery($sql, $params, $executionTime) {
        $queryInfo = [
            'sql' => $sql,
            'params' => $params,
            'execution_time' => $executionTime,
            'timestamp' => microtime(true)
        ];
        
        $this->queries[] = $queryInfo;
        
        if ($executionTime > 1.0) { // 慢查詢警告
            $this->logger->warning('慢查詢檢測', $queryInfo);
        }
    }
    
    public function getQueryReport() {
        return [
            'total_queries' => count($this->queries),
            'total_time' => array_sum(array_column($this->queries, 'execution_time')),
            'slow_queries' => array_filter($this->queries, function($q) {
                return $q['execution_time'] > 1.0;
            }),
            'queries' => $this->queries
        ];
    }
}
```

## WebSocket調試

### WebSocket連接監控
```php
class WebSocketDebugger {
    private $connections = [];
    private $messages = [];
    
    public function onConnection($connectionId, $userInfo) {
        $this->connections[$connectionId] = [
            'user_info' => $userInfo,
            'connected_at' => time(),
            'message_count' => 0
        ];
        
        $this->log('WebSocket連接', [
            'connection_id' => $connectionId,
            'user_info' => $userInfo
        ]);
    }
    
    public function onMessage($connectionId, $message) {
        $this->connections[$connectionId]['message_count']++;
        
        $messageInfo = [
            'connection_id' => $connectionId,
            'message' => $message,
            'timestamp' => microtime(true)
        ];
        
        $this->messages[] = $messageInfo;
        
        $this->log('WebSocket訊息', $messageInfo);
    }
    
    public function onDisconnection($connectionId) {
        if (isset($this->connections[$connectionId])) {
            $connectionInfo = $this->connections[$connectionId];
            $connectionInfo['disconnected_at'] = time();
            $connectionInfo['duration'] = time() - $connectionInfo['connected_at'];
            
            $this->log('WebSocket斷開', $connectionInfo);
            unset($this->connections[$connectionId]);
        }
    }
}
```

## AI API調試

### OpenAI API調試
```php
class AIDebugger {
    private $requests = [];
    private $logger;
    
    public function logRequest($prompt, $response, $executionTime, $tokenUsage) {
        $requestInfo = [
            'prompt' => substr($prompt, 0, 200) . '...', // 截取前200字符
            'response' => substr($response, 0, 200) . '...',
            'execution_time' => $executionTime,
            'token_usage' => $tokenUsage,
            'timestamp' => date('c')
        ];
        
        $this->requests[] = $requestInfo;
        $this->logger->info('AI API請求', $requestInfo);
        
        if ($executionTime > 10.0) {
            $this->logger->warning('AI API響應緩慢', $requestInfo);
        }
    }
    
    public function getUsageReport() {
        return [
            'total_requests' => count($this->requests),
            'total_tokens' => array_sum(array_column($this->requests, 'token_usage')),
            'average_response_time' => array_sum(array_column($this->requests, 'execution_time')) / count($this->requests),
            'recent_requests' => array_slice($this->requests, -10)
        ];
    }
}
```

## 前端調試

### JavaScript錯誤捕獲
```javascript
class FrontendDebugger {
    constructor() {
        this.errors = [];
        this.setupErrorHandlers();
    }
    
    setupErrorHandlers() {
        window.addEventListener('error', (event) => {
            this.logError({
                type: 'javascript_error',
                message: event.message,
                filename: event.filename,
                lineno: event.lineno,
                colno: event.colno,
                stack: event.error ? event.error.stack : null,
                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
            });
        });
        
        window.addEventListener('unhandledrejection', (event) => {
            this.logError({
                type: 'promise_rejection',
                reason: event.reason,
                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
            });
        });
    }
    
    logError(errorInfo) {
        this.errors.push(errorInfo);
        console.error('前端錯誤:', errorInfo);
        
        // 發送到後端
        fetch('/api/debug/frontend-error', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
            body: JSON.stringify(errorInfo)
        });
    }
    
    getErrorReport() {
        return {
            total_errors: this.errors.length,
            recent_errors: this.errors.slice(-10),
            error_types: this.groupErrorsByType()
        };
    }
}
```

### WebSocket調試工具
```javascript
class WebSocketDebugger {
    constructor(websocket) {
        this.ws = websocket;
        this.messages = [];
        this.setupDebugHandlers();
    }
    
    setupDebugHandlers() {
        const originalSend = this.ws.send;
        this.ws.send = (data) => {
            this.logMessage('sent', data);
            return originalSend.call(this.ws, data);
        };
        
        this.ws.addEventListener('message', (event) => {
            this.logMessage('received', event.data);
        });
        
        this.ws.addEventListener('error', (event) => {
            this.logError('WebSocket錯誤', event);
        });
    }
    
    logMessage(direction, data) {
        const messageInfo = {
            direction: direction,
            data: data,
            timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
            size: new Blob([data]).size
        };
        
        this.messages.push(messageInfo);
        console.log(`WebSocket ${direction}:`, messageInfo);
    }
}
```

## 系統監控

### 系統資源監控
```php
class SystemMonitor {
    public function getSystemStats() {
        return [
            'memory_usage' => memory_get_usage(true),
            'memory_peak' => memory_get_peak_usage(true),
            'cpu_load' => sys_getloadavg(),
            'disk_usage' => disk_free_space('.'),
            'active_connections' => $this->getActiveConnections(),
            'database_connections' => $this->getDatabaseConnections()
        ];
    }
    
    public function checkSystemHealth() {
        $stats = $this->getSystemStats();
        $issues = [];
        
        if ($stats['memory_usage'] > 512 * 1024 * 1024) { // 512MB
            $issues[] = '內存使用過高';
        }
        
        if ($stats['cpu_load'][0] > 2.0) {
            $issues[] = 'CPU負載過高';
        }
        
        if ($stats['disk_usage'] < 1024 * 1024 * 1024) { // 1GB
            $issues[] = '磁盤空間不足';
        }
        
        return [
            'healthy' => empty($issues),
            'issues' => $issues,
            'stats' => $stats
        ];
    }
}
```

